## File & Import Conventions

```typescript
// Imports order:
// 1. React/Next
// 2. Third-party (gsap, lucide, etc.)
// 3. Components (@/components/...)
// 4. Hooks (@/hooks/...)
// 5. Lib/Utils (@/lib/...)
// 6. Types (@/types/...)
```

### Path Aliases (tsconfig)
```
@/ → root of project
```

