- All UI labels, headings, body text: **Bahasa Indonesia**
- WhatsApp number: **085328613613** → link: `https://wa.me/6285328613613`
- Instagram: `https://www.instagram.com/glassboardindonesia/`
- Brand name: **NADAZ** (all caps in display, mixed in body)
- Company: **PT. Arta Prima Glassindo**
- Area layanan: **Jabodetabek** (Jakarta, Bogor, Depok, Tangerang, Bekasi)
- USP: "Free ongkir & pemasangan seluruh Jabodetabek"

