## Image Handling

```tsx
// Always use next/image
import Image from "next/image"

// Hero images: priority={true}
// All others: lazy (default)
// Always provide alt text in Indonesian
// Aspect ratios: products 4:3, portfolio 16:9, clients 3:2
```

Placeholder for missing images:
```tsx
// Use a div with gradient placeholder
<div className="aspect-[4/3] bg-gradient-to-br from-[--color-brand-navy] to-[--color-brand-dark] rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center">
  <span className="text-[--color-brand-muted] text-sm">Foto segera hadir</span>
</div>
```

---

## Accessibility

- All interactive elements: visible focus ring
- Icon-only buttons: `aria-label` in Indonesian
- Section headings: proper `h1` → `h2` → `h3` hierarchy
- Images: meaningful alt text
- Color contrast: minimum WCAG AA

---

## Do NOT

- ❌ Add placeholder/lorem ipsum in final copy — use real Indonesian copy
- ❌ Use `any` TypeScript type without comment
- ❌ Forget `"use client"` on components using hooks/GSAP
- ❌ Use `window` directly — guard with `typeof window !== "undefined"`
- ❌ Add random decorative animations — every motion must serve UX
- ❌ Hardcode pixel values — use Tailwind spacing scale
- ❌ Skip mobile responsive — always test at `sm:` breakpoint
